  "title": "Technical Support Assistant (Up to $3000 / 5 days / Joo Koon)",
  "description": "<p>Job Title: Technical Support Assistant (M1-1027)<br />Location: Joo Koon<br />Working Hours: Mon-Fri 8am-5.10pm<br />Salary: $2800-$3000<br /><br />Responsibilities<br />• Perform regular checks in inventory software system to ensure inventories are in place<br />• Perform regular repairs and maintenance of yard and workshop tools and equipment<br />• Help maintain the tool room through 5S initiatives and good housekeeping practices<br /><br />Requirement<br />• Relevant technical certification<br />• Basic technical knowledge on tooling and vehicle maintenance<br />• Computer literate to navigate inventory system and Microsoft Office suite required on the job<br />• Class 3 driving license. Candidates with forklift driving license will be an added advantage<br />• Able to work with minimal supervision<br />• Able to work overtime including weekends</p>",
